ᱜᱚᱢᱵᱷᱟᱨᱤ ᱫᱮᱵᱤ (᱑᱙᱒᱒-᱘ ᱡᱟᱱᱩᱣᱟᱨᱤ ᱒᱐᱑᱓) ᱦᱤᱢᱟᱪᱚᱲ ᱯᱨᱚᱫᱮᱥ ᱯᱚᱱᱚᱛ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ  ᱵᱤᱞᱟᱥᱯᱩᱨ ᱦᱚᱱᱚᱛ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢᱟᱱ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱥᱮᱨᱮᱧ ᱵᱟᱰᱳᱦᱤ, <ref>{{cite web | title = London Olympics silver medallist Vijay Kumar conferred Rs 1 crore and Himachal Gaurav Award|publisher=Economic Times | url = http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2012-08-15/news/33216832_1_london-olympics-silver-himachal-gaurav-award-vijay-kumar |date=15 Aug 2012| accessdate = 2014-08-02 }}</ref> ᱯᱷᱠᱞᱳᱨᱤᱥᱴᱴ ᱟᱨ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱠᱩᱲᱤ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ, ᱦᱤᱢᱟᱪᱚᱲ ᱯᱨᱚᱫᱮᱥ ᱨᱮ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱟ.ᱨᱤᱪᱟ.ᱞᱤ ᱨᱮ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱢᱮᱥᱟ ᱟ.ᱰᱤ ᱛᱮᱫ ᱜᱮ ᱮᱱᱮᱢ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱠᱟᱫᱟ ᱾<ref name="Jeratha1995">{{cite book|author=Ashoka Jerath|title=The Splendour of Himalayan Art and Culture|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IQDkxM0GTw4C&pg=PA151|year=1995|publisher=Indus Publishing|isbn=978-81-7387-034-7|pages=151–}}</ref>᱒᱐᱑᱑ ᱥᱟᱞᱮ ᱨᱮ ᱥᱚᱸᱜᱤᱛ ᱱᱟᱴᱚᱠ ᱮᱠᱟᱰᱮᱢᱤ ᱯᱟᱥᱴᱟ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱴᱟᱜᱳᱨ ᱮᱠᱟᱰᱮᱢᱤ ᱥᱤᱨᱯᱟ ᱮ ᱧᱟᱢ ᱟᱠᱟᱫᱟᱭᱮ, ᱥᱮᱨᱮᱧ ᱨᱮ, ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱨᱮ , ᱜᱟᱭᱟᱱ ᱞᱟ.ᱜᱤᱫ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱱᱟᱥᱱᱟᱞ ᱮᱠᱟᱰᱮᱢᱤ ᱥᱤᱨᱯᱟ ᱧᱟᱢ ᱞᱮᱫᱟᱭᱮ ᱾<ref>{{cite web | title = Sangeet Natak Akademi Ratna and Akademi Puraskar | url = http://sangeetnatak.gov.in/sna/tagoreawards.htm | quote = ".. a one-time honour of Tagore Samman to be awarded to 100 persons of the age of 75 years and above who have made significant contribution in the field of performing arts." | publisher = Sangeet Natak Akademi | date = 2011 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url-status = dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140707094419/http://sangeetnatak.gov.in/sna/tagoreawards.htm | archivedate = 7 July 2014 | df = dmy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=List of recipients of Tagore Akademi Puraskar|url = http://pib.nic.in/archieve/others/2012/apr/d2012042301.pdf |publisher= [[Press Information Bureau]], Government of India|accessdate = 2014-08-02 }}</ref>





